responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "D179172441CF0D98334A82859FA0D8A8", "Keep away from the gates, friend. Goblins have been at the walls non-stop, capturing or killing anyone they can get their claws on. Captain Avenmoor has a plan, but it\'s a struggle to wait and see.")
